snippet.title: Game & Watch - Crab Grab (c)1984 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: Algestam and Ryan Holtz got Nintendo's Crab Grab emulated. This is one of only 2 games in the Super Color series (Spitball Sparky, already emulated, being the other)  The game has an original arcade puzzle/action game feel to it, although the controls can be a bit unresponsive, which cost me a few lives in this video.  Artwork was done by DarthMarino and can be found on his Google Drive ( https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY?usp=sharing )
